,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佢係住私樓但呃你住公屋呢 ?</blockquote><br />\n我試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026df66b1a6e05996de190e22f7a85c089f940e8","tid":448360,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佢係住私樓但呃你住公屋呢 ?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9aab5f78b0c9e0bd1b18599c107ce184de1b33c5","tid":448360,"uid":139322,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:55:40.000Z","msg":"咁撚多連登仔開post扮女人<br />\n係咪恨女恨到痴撚晒線"},{"pid":"b72726bf0c665bd1e0537cdf3730968f195a2d14","tid":448360,"uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佢係住私樓但呃你住公屋呢 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有大學同學就真係咁<br />\n住簿扶林私樓，一千呎，呃女朋友住華富邨"},{"pid":"23efd377b9ff6824dc2d7286f712c7b8a90b2f81","tid":448360,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:57:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果佢係住私樓但呃你住公屋呢 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有大學同學就真係咁<br />\n住簿扶林私樓，一千呎，呃女朋友住華富邨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話避免未來老婆和女友，因為錢而愛他。<br />\n所以要保護自己。<br />\n住薄扶林千呎私樓，扮住公屋。"},{"pid":"bbce6d02430a2c7eec8384b469f3e6492088eecf","tid":448360,"uid":72647,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:57:17.000Z","msg":"男朋友又係呃我，佢話佢做飯店，點知原來係開酒店"},{"pid":"f71e26e466a7d76f54f4e07275d2e5e7a59ed1a0","tid":448360,"uid":38651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佢係住私樓但呃你住公屋呢 ?</blockquote><br />\n諗起個笑話<br />\n佢住私樓但呃你住公屋 你覺得無問題<br />\n因為你係鍾意佢個人 唔係鍾意佢啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢住公屋但呃你住私樓 你覺得有問題<br />\n因為有無錢唔係問題 最緊要誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647360d57d85ae18890990df0a1b6646550d00a5","tid":448360,"uid":16922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl